snippet.title: Stunt Island gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Stunt Island, Dos PC game produced by Walt Disney in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/stunt-island/710/
Watching the intro and trying out a few stunts in this unusual flight simulator.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
